entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, it's 'mpressive, right? It's too bad most of the BDs we do here are only good for floggin' the log…
Anyway, you ready to do this, look at your rec?
OK, OK... Go ahead... Just need T-Bug to link in.
Whoa, whoa, whoa. Who?
Runner from my crew, security specialist. She'll tell me what to look for while we analyze. No problem, I hope?
Actually, it IS a problem.
Judy, T-Bug's a professional, discreet to a fault. You can trust her.
Relax, Judy. Everything'll be fine.
Please, Judy...
You don't quite grasp the risks I took by lettin' you in here. What I'm risking pokin' around with this stuff.
We're all takin' risks here. That's the job. So either T-Bug patches in, or I'm on my way out.
Judy, please.
Hey, V. What's happenin'?
Bug, listen. I got some useful footage from Konpeki Plaza. It's a braindance.
Konpeki? Ohhh, thought as much…
Someone there with you?
Judy and Evelyn. They're chill. They're helping me work through this BD.
Listen... need your help. Got no clue what to look for once I'm in.
Unimportant, Bug. Please focus. Need your help – got no clue what I'm supposed to look for once I'm in.
entries.maleVariant: Unimportant, T-Bug. Please focus. Need your help – got no clue what I'm supposed to look for once I'm in.

entries.femaleVariant: All right, see if I can walk you through it.
Uh-huh... All right – you gonna tell me what this is about?
Jackin' into your tech now.
You can trust T-Bug.
Relax, Judy. Everything'll be fine.
Why? 'Cause you say so?
I'd never expose you to any danger. You know that…
Evelyn? I won't get a damn thing out of this without T-Bug.
Judy, please...
Ev, she wants to bring a 'runner in. What part of that don't you understand?
entries.maleVariant: Ev, he wants to bring a 'runner in. What part of that don't you understand?

entries.femaleVariant: How do I know she'll only perch in this footage, observe, not fuck with anything?
Me – I'm your guarantee.
Yeah, right...
Help me this one last time. I promise everything'll work out – just like we planned.
Heh, fine. Call 'er, let's get this over with.
OK, V. Call T-Bug and we'll dive in.
Mh, you've gotta give me access. Opening port 1779... Secure protocol? Good, I'm goin' in. Should be getting my request…
...now.
Got it. You ready?
Millisec. OK, connection confirmed, now some quick temp ICE and... we're clear.
Fire 'er up, Judy.
Evelyn?
Doesn't matter. You ready?
Judy and Evelyn.
[Call T-Bug]
Ready to dance.
Slow, deep breaths. Your cortisol and adrenaline spiked, but the soft activated your hormone blockers. Nothin' happened, you're alive and well.
That was... too much.
Could've warned me...
That was... too much. Felt... could feel the guy's... pain, his stress, his... hope? Hope wrapped up in somethin' else…
Mhm. Probably took a booster just before.
You'll be fine. Got everything set up. Let's switch over to editing mode.
That flash of... intense shock. Can still feel it, I-I-I remember... Fuck, that last second... Coulda warned me how much it hurts to die.
entries.maleVariant: That flash of... intense shock. Can still feel it, I remember... Fuck, that last second... Ya coulda warned me how much it hurts to die.

entries.femaleVariant: Trust me, real death hurts much, much more.
Not what we agreed, Ev.
Judy, please...
Ev, she wants to bring a 'runner in. What part of that don't you understand?
entries.maleVariant: Ev, he wants to bring a 'runner in. What part of that don't you understand?

entries.femaleVariant: How do I know she'll only slip into this footage?
Me – I'm your guarantee.
Yeah, right...

Help me this one last time. I promise everything'll work out – just like we planned.
Aaaah!
Not so sure about that...
Dunno, I... Let's take a break. Still feel like that kid when... Yeah, think I'm done.
entries.maleVariant: Dunno, I... Let's take a break. Still feel like that kid when... Phew, yeah, think I'm done.

entries.femaleVariant: V, there's no time. Get it together, please.
Everything all right, V?
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Digame" b="" a=", how ya feelin'?"/>
